Package event

Class Event

  • java.lang.Object
    • event.Event
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    A2SUpdatedEvent, AdminBroadcastEvent, ChatMessageEvent, DeployableDamagedEvent, LayerInfoUpdatedEvent, NewGameEvent, PlayerBannedEvent, PlayerConnectedEvent, PlayerDamagedEvent, PlayerDiedEvent, PlayerDisconnectedEvent, PlayerKickedEvent, PlayerListUpdatedEvent, PlayerPossessEvent, PlayerRevivedEvent, PlayerUnPossessEvent, PlayerWarnedEvent, PlayerWoundedEvent, PossessedAdminCameraEvent, RoundWinnerEvent, ServerTickRateEvent, SquadCreatedEvent, SquadListUpdatedEvent, SteamidConnectedEvent, UnpossessedAdminCameraEvent
    public abstract class Event
extends Object
    Author:
    Robert Engle An abstract class defining an event that can occur. Events that occur from the log parser have a date/time, type, and chain ID. Events that occur from anywhere else do not have a chain ID.

        public Optional<Integer> getChainID()
